{"tid":828822,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人個鼻成日好似好多鼻屎咁？","createTime":"2018-09-20T03:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T09:20:01.000Z","uid":96331,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcd653bf4b2f32418f4a8ee0a73bea481c817a3","tid":828822,"uid":96331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始，只要出完街就會覺得個鼻入面好多鼻屎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係去完旺角、銅鑼灣呢啲旺區，<br />\n行到咁上下就會feel到個鼻越嚟越多嘢，入面好似腫咗舊嘢咁。<br />\n最誇張嘅係試過行行下覺得成日有陣臭臭地嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，雖然唔算濃烈，但就硬係有陣味。但附近明明無嘢係臭，都唔係自己汗味，最後撩咗啲臭屎出嚟就無再聞到。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都會係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808f0f8b37c610ae1ea13044b162be865e7e1811","tid":828822,"uid":86337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:26:39.000Z","msg":"有鼻息肉 成日都有野頂住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5939bd9479998a64027c61c1fcefdacb9ada5413","tid":828822,"uid":86651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得我鼻屎耳屎牙屎都得 其實係咪身體邊到虧左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7738da4ba50fdcc382b7dbb068ee9e58cbed566","tid":828822,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"有無人食完唔同嘅野啲鼻屎會有唔同味"},{"pid":"4778e78ff0447a1951d6587dc8ff6a4fa93e72b4","tid":828822,"uid":103012,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"去完啲空氣差嘅地方之後個鼻一定會好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到好多鼻屎喺入面 之後一定要匿入公廁入面撩乾淨佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得撩會好辛苦<br />\n撩到粒大鼻屎會好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f